  "Combine the calcium cation with the hydroxide anion to get calcium hydroxide": "",
  "2HCl + Ca(OH)2 -> CaCl2 + 2H2O. The cation Ca2+ from the base pairs with the Cl- anion from the acid to form calcium chloride (CaCl2).": "",
